snippet: Stacy Lewis made six birdies for a six-under-par 66, taking a two-stroke lead in the HSBC Women’s Champions in Singapore.
abstract: Reigning LPGA player of the year Stacy Lewis takes second-round lead at HSBC Women's Champions in Singapore.
lead_paragraph: Stacy Lewis made six birdies for a six-under-par 66, taking a two-stroke lead in the HSBC Women’s Champions in Singapore.
